~~~ 0.5 ~~~
April 8, 2008

* fix DST parsing issue.
* fix ToLocal/ToUTC time formatting issue.
* remove supporting for leap min/second so that the module will be sure
  support both RFC3339 and ISO8601 fully.
* Add dateutil so that the module supports another 10+ different time
  input formattime, such as '11:30 am", "April 10, 2008', etc.
* fix timezone parsing issue by using pytz as the base timezone
  parsing module.


